&lt;h2 id=&#34;equipped-with-hetsyn&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#equipped-with-hetsyn&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Equipped with HetSyn&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In HetSyn, we replace the uniform time constant with synapse-specific decay factors and model the reset process as a negative current injection. Each synaptic current now evolves independently over time, allowing the neuron to integrate information at multiple timescales:&lt;/p&gt;
